sentences: Kim Ian (Korean: 김이안; Hanja: 金李安) (born Kim Bo-ryung on March 28, 1987) is a South Korean actor and singer.
Kim made his first appearance in f(x)'s endorsement of K-Swiss's 2010 Winter Collection.
Kim then made his first variety appearance on MBC's 2011 Idol Star Athletics Championships.
He was on Team A with label-mates Shinee, Super Junior, TRAX, and The Grace - Dana & Sunday
In 2011, Kim starred in the musical Singin' In The Rain as Donghyun.
In 2012 he starred in his second musical Fantasy Couple as Jang Chul Soo with label-mate Sunday of The Grace.
In 2012 he starred in his second musical Fantasy Couple as Jang Chul Soo with label-mate Sunday of The Grace.
The musical was based on the highly rated 2006 drama Fantasy Couple.
In July 2012, Kim was confirmed to play Na Chul Soo in To The Beautiful You, the Korean adaptation of Hana-Kimi.
In January 2013, Kim starred as the male lead in Girls' Generation's music video for their lead single "I Got a Boy".
